  <li><strong>Guaranteed Satisfaction:</strong> Our service is backed by a 100% satisfaction guarantee.</li>
</ul>

<h3>How to Prepare for Post-Construction Cleaning</h3>
<p>Before your cleaning team arrives, consider these preparations to streamline the process:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Clear Access:</strong> Ensure the team has clear paths to all areas that need cleaning.</li>
  <li><strong>Remove Personal Items:</strong> Protect your belongings by storing them safely away from dusty areas.</li>
  <li><strong>Communicate Clearly:</strong> Discuss any special requests or areas of concern with your cleaning team beforehand.</li>
</ul>

